{
  "id": "adv_main_02_09_01",
  "title": "東京編2章16話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――祭典・I-UNITYのトーナメント抽選会当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Day of the I-UNITY tournament draw",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.03333333507180214,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2366.666664928198,
          "startTime": 2.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 2.4
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 2.4
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 7.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "うわあ……すっごい人！\nここにいるみんなが、出場するアイドルなんだよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa! There are so many people!\nAll the idols here are contestants‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。I-UNITYへの参加を決めた事務所は\n業界全体の約半分って話だからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. It seems around half of all the agencies\nin the industry have decided to participate in I-UNITY.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 18.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "NEXT VENUSグランプリとは全然規模感が違う\nそれにみんな、新人アイドルって訳でもない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The scale is entirely different from the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix.\nOn top of that‚ not all of them are newcomer idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 31.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "テレビで見たことある人も、沢山いる\nさすがに少し、緊張するわね……あれ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve seen a lot of them on TV.\nI can’t help feeling a little nervous… Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5266.666666700001,
          "startTime": 36.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 36.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "……あっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tri-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 38.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 38.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん！\n優ちゃんに、すみれちゃんも！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui!\nYu and Sumire!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 42.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "さくら……みんな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura… girls…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 45.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりトリエルも来てたんだね\nこんなにいっぱい人がいるのに、再会出来るなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I knew you’d be here.\nWith all the people around‚ I can’t believe we ran into each other.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 54.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "それに……\n三人とも元気そうで、凄く安心したよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not to mention…\nI’m so relieved to see the three of you looking great.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 57.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "……\nみんなも、やっぱり出場するのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…\nSo you’re all competing as well then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 62.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。開催に当たっては、思うところもあるけど\n私達アイドルは、ファンを楽しませるのが本望だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Some things about the event don’t sit right with us‚\nbut we’re idols; our job is to entertain our fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 74.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "そのために出場して、勝ち上がるつもりよ\nたとえスリクスが……そしてトリエルが立ち塞がっても",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why we’re going to compete and win.\nWhether IIIX… or TRINITYAiLE stands in our way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 78.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 78.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "……ふふっ。莉央さんらしくて、全然ブレへんなぁ\nそれに、まだそんな風に言ってくれるんやね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Heheh. I wouldn’t expect less from you‚ Rio. You never waver.\nAlso‚ I didn’t expect you to still treat us the same way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 86.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "……当たり前じゃないですか\nみなさんは私達にとって、ライバルなんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why wouldn’t we?\nWe look up to you as our rivals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 92.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "どうして私達がこんなことになったかは\n今更、とやかく言ってもしかたないです。でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It doesn’t matter now\nhow things ended up this way. But still…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 100.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "トーナメントでぶつかり、同じステージに立てば\n私達は正々堂々、戦うだけです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we run into each other on the same stage at the tournament‚\nwe’ll battle you fair and square.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "うん。だから、頑張ろうね！\n一緒のステージに立てるのを、楽しみにしてる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. So let’s all do our best!\nLooking forward to competing together on the same stage!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 114.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "さくらさん、琴乃さん……\n二人とも、なんでそんなに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura‚ Kotono…\nWhy are you two so…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 119.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "それがこの子達の純粋な気持ちなんでしょう？\nいろいろ事情は察している上での……ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure that’s how they genuinely feel.\nYou know… taking into consideration all the circumstances.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 126.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "でも私達は違う\n必要以上になれ合うつもりはないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But not us.\nWe’ve no intention of being overly familiar with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 131.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "……はい。もちろん、私達もそのつもりです\nアイドルとして、勝ちにいきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. We don’t intend to either.\nAs idols‚ we’ll go for the win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalout-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 138.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "自分達がしてきたことを背負って、正々堂々戦う\nその覚悟はしてきましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll carry the burden of our actions and battle you fair and square.\nWe’re prepared for that.",
        "id": ""
      },
